  <brief_title>Acute Hemodynamic and Biological Effects of ECP and Exercise</brief_title>
  <official_title>Acute Cardiovascular Effects of External Counterpulsation (ECP) in Comparison With Physical Exercise in Healthy Individuals</official_title>
  <sponsors>
